{"tid":1829194,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[賀年獻禮]大年初三聽證會！德國戰線下半場開波！！","createTime":"2020-01-18T13:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T00:11:17.000Z","uid":230840,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ea685cffb63c25ad5d19ae41b3247b82d490eafc","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"咁多位deadline fighters ，唔知你哋仲記唔記得之前有三份要你哋簽嘅德國聯署？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而第一份夠數嘅議題將會喺大年初三(27/1)十一點進行聽證會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，內容有關停止香港人道危機同埋制裁香港警察同主事官員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣唔單止有聯署人同發起人發言，仲會有德國嘅官員去回答國會議員質詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會議內容係全德文，我哋會記錄低跟住翻譯返畀大家知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，詳情可以留意番Germany stands with Hong Kong嘅facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/germanyswhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgermanyswhk%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1M4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=010ab3cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/germanyswhk/</a><br />\n嗰陣會有直播，學緊或者識德文隻手足可以click入去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，好多謝各位有份簽名嘅咁多位香港人同有份推post嘅kol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋會繼續打呢條德國戰線，聽日喺柏林同法蘭克福都會有手足舉行集會，兄弟爬山各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> Freiheit f&uuml;r Hongkongers</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ab23857833cbc2b65775c597673f8fe0af48a7ce","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:32:44.000Z","msg":"自推十連(1/10)"},{"pid":"3f4c89be789b7aa03718e0eead7e880c1230d4a5","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOcFDkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOcFDkD.jpg&h=0efba5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2/10)"},{"pid":"3570ec82095b2f14369974905fcafe3b94583680","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"天滅中共(3/10)"},{"pid":"b16f9e94348841bc93bd4e4ed8cfbfb476bd2a26","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"解散警隊，刻不容緩<br />\n(4/10)"},{"pid":"07de321324913a662cf90f92dcaacc5be81bbf62","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"by any means necessary (5/10)"},{"pid":"1aa1465be59a6634c0cf762e0e767c52aca42f0c","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n（6/10）"},{"pid":"458f3ce5097317b62cd82bac1cc7aeaac06541de","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"請停止捉鬼（7/10）"},{"pid":"bc6ca64a1281adacde91a517a3208f6d48931b2e","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"Fight for freedom<br />\nstand with Hong Kong (8/10)"},{"pid":"b02f2e7b2f1aa7919a628fbad247904059c80a33","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家（9/10）"},{"pid":"9d88eed2056ace08dac8b35d4a68ddfdd075ff2b","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"我願榮光歸香港（10/10）"},{"pid":"c250e67ad633284e79ac43edeedc883b16e8ea7d","tid":1829194,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":