g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da24106b610308387f171728a4004f90047d829","tid":1829194,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"推熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea68013f954be1a7236ba9fbdd505b76c1b24dc","tid":1829194,"uid":300950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b8d8376178189c9ad4b805d44f7120f4e96f6417","tid":1829194,"uid":230840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T21:40:01.000Z","msg":"柏林-公眾聽證會<br />\nPublic Hearing at Berlin Bundestag<br />\n<br />\n聽朝十一點(香港時間下午六點)，有關「停止香港人道危機，制裁主事官員和香港警察」嘅聯署就會係國會進行公眾聽證會。會議將以德語舉行，由兩名港人代表(發起人和聯署人)出席和發言，政府相關官員亦會出席會議，回答議員質詢。會議錄影將於同日德國時間下午四點(香港時間夜晚十一點)喺<a href=\"http://www.bundestag.de\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bundestag.de&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1M4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=56834ca0\" target=\"_blank\">www.bundestag.de</a>播放，稍後我們亦會上載附上中英文字幕的影片。<br />\n<br />\n登記咗嘅朋友就記得帶埋護照（身份證明文件）出席！<br />\n<br />\nThe Public Hearing about the Petition, &quot;Stop the humanitarian crisis in Hong Kong, Sanction the responsible officials and HKPF&quot; is going to hold on tomorrow morning, 11 a.m.( Hong Kong's 6 p.m.) at Bundestag. At Germany's 4 p.m.(Hong Kong's 11p.m.)  , the video of the hearing will be uploaded onto <a href=\"http://www.bundestag.de\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bundestag.de&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1M4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=56834ca0\" target=\"_blank\">www.bundestag.de</a>. We will upload the video with Chinese &amp; English subtitles afterwards.<br />\n<br />\nPeople who have registered, please remember to bring your passport or any personal identification card with you. See you tomorrow!"}}